<div id="review_3989611952" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3989611952" />
    <a title="Tavleen Kaur (Travelling Through Words)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32793447-tavleen-kaur-travelling-through-words"><img alt="Tavleen Kaur (Travelling Through Words)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1639424505p2/32793447.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3989611952?book_show_action=true">May 08, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tavleen Kaur (Travelling Through Words)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tavleen Kaur (Travelling Through Words)" href="/user/show/32793447-tavleen-kaur-travelling-through-words">Tavleen Kaur (Travelling Through Words)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781559702355" href="/book/show/117238.The_Good_Person_of_Szechwan">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32793447-tavleen-kaur-travelling-through-words?shelf=read-in-2021">read-in-2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32793447-tavleen-kaur-travelling-through-words?shelf=college-reads">college-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3989611952" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10193214452015408692">&apos;The Good Person of Szechwan&apos; by Bertolt Brecht is an interesting play all about whether there are good people left in the world and how if one is a good person, they just get taken advantage of. It is set in a society that is being torn by war and everyone is looking out for themselves. The poor and middle class is struggling. <br/><br/>The main character Shen Teh is an interesting character. She has to fend for herself by prostituition but later becomes a business woman. Being a &apos;good&apos; person, she gets </span>
  <span id="freeText10193214452015408692" style="display:none">'The Good Person of Szechwan' by Bertolt Brecht is an interesting play all about whether there are good people left in the world and how if one is a good person, they just get taken advantage of. It is set in a society that is being torn by war and everyone is looking out for themselves. The poor and middle class is struggling. <br /><br />The main character Shen Teh is an interesting character. She has to fend for herself by prostituition but later becomes a business woman. Being a 'good' person, she gets taken advantage of by many people. She plays a double role by disguising herself as her male cousin. In her male disguise, she is more authoritative and stern with people. The double role is a commentary on the different way people treat men and women.<br /><br />Some incidents in the play were quite illogical and too convenient. But overall, this is a good play that does address some valid themes.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10193214452015408692" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


